headline: Nike Stock Stuck On Harsh Downtrend Ahead Of Earnings; New CEO Aims For Turnaround
summary: Nike stock hasn't been able to attract many buyers amid a slowdown in growth, but CEO Elliot Hill is optimistic about a turnaround.
